steps.name: click 'Manage Jenkins' link from Main page
Click Manage Nodes on ManageJenkins Page
Input Node name 'NameFor Delete' in field
Click on the 'Permanent Agent' Radio button on the New node page
Click on the 'Create' button on the New node page
Open 'NameFor Delete' node in dropdown menu
